items.name: Alfajores de Lucuma (10 per packet)
items.description: Seasonal item! Hop into the season with our Alfajores de Lucuma! 10 buttery cookies filled with dreamy lucuma dulce de leche- the perfect combo of sweet & creamy goodness.

items.name: Alfajores- 6-pack combo
items.description: OUR 6-PACK COMBO! Treat yourself or that special someone with a great selection of our favorite alfajores: Lemon, Classic & Chocolate!

items.name: Alfajores- Chocolate (1 dozen- packet)
items.description: A dark chocolate coating is a perfect complement to our butter cookie filled with creamy dulce de leche. To finish it off, a sprinkle of Peruvian sea salt.

items.name: Alfajores- Classic (1 dozen- packet)
items.description: DESTINO has always taken great pleasure in sharing our alfajores with our community. Our family recipe stems from years of inspiration from both the Schenk and Castellanos families.

items.name: Alfajores- Gingerbread (1 dozen- packet)
items.description: Seasonal item! Satisfy your sweet tooth this holiday season with our delightful GINGERBREAD ALFAJORES!

items.description: DESTINO has always taken great pleasure in sharing our alfajores with our community- now we offer our Gluten Free Alfajor!

items.name: Alfajores- Lemon (1 dozen packet)
items.description: Our classic butter cookies with dulce de leche are blanketed with a vibrant & tangy lemon royal icing- for extra deliciousness!

items.name: Empanadas- Argentine Beef (frozen- 4 pack)
items.description: Box of four frozen empanadas. Our recipe is based on a traditional Argentine beef empanada- ground beef, pimiento stuffed olives, egg and golden raisins!

items.name: Empanadas- Caribbean Pork (frozen- 4 pack)
items.description: Box of four frozen empanadas. Our Caribbean pork empanadas are delicious and addicting! These empanadas feature ground pork, black mission figs and a medley of spices!

items.name: Empanadas- Huacatay Chicken (frozen- 4 pack)
items.description: Our huacatay chicken empanadas are divine! Savory Peruvian black mint with corn and spinach are truly satisfying- leaving you craving for more.

items.name: Empanadas- Lomo Saltado (frozen- 4 pack)
items.description: LOMO SALTADO EMPANADAS! If you love Lomo Saltado like we do- you would love this spin on a Peruvian classic! Top sirloin / aji amarillo / red onion / roasted potatoes.

items.name: Empanadas- Peruvian Chicken (frozen- 4 pack)
items.description: Box of four frozen empanadas. Our chicken empanadas are inspired by a Peruvian classic "Aji de Gallina." Our recipe features free range chicken mixed with a delicious aji amarillo-cream sauce.

items.name: Empanadas- Salmon (frozen- 4 pack)
items.description: Box of four frozen empanadas. Our Limited Edition Salmon empanadas are a treat! These empanadas feature local King salmon marinated with a sweet & tangy tamarind-panela glaze are addicting!

items.description: Box of four frozen empanadas. Our vegetarian empanadas have become one of biggest sellers- featuring hearts of palms, aji amarillo, parmesan & mozzarella cheeses.
